{\rtf1\ansi\uc1{\*\generator WTS5;}\adeflang1025\adeff0\deff0\stshfdbch0\stshfloch0\stshfhich0\deflang1033\deflangfe1033{\fonttbl{\f0\fcharset0 Times New Roman;}{\f1\fcharset0 Latha;}{\f2\fcharset0 Arial;}{\f3\fbidi\fcharset177 Arial;}}{\colortbl ;\red128\green0\blue128;}{\stylesheet {\s2\ltrpar\qc \rtlch\fcs1\alang1046\af1\ltrch\fcs0\lang1046\langnp1046\langfe1033\langfenp1033\f0\fs36\cf1\b \slink62\sbasedon0\snext21 Title;}}\plain\langnp1033\langfenp1033\ltrdoc\fcs1\af0\afs24\acf0\fcs0\f0\fs24\cf0{\info\uc1{\upr{\*\ud{\author \u67?\u111?\u112?\u121?\u114?\u105?\u103?\u104?\u116?\u32?\u169?\u32?\u50?\u48?\u50?\u53?\u32?\u87?\u97?\u116?\u99?\u104?\u32?\u84?\u111?\u119?\u101?\u114?\u32?\u66?\u105?\u98?\u108?\u101?\u32?\u97?\u110?\u100?\u32?\u84?\u114?\u97?\u99?\u116?\u32?\u83?\u111?\u99?\u105?\u101?\u116?\u121?\u32?\u111?\u102?\u32?\u80?\u101?\u110?\u110?\u115?\u121?\u108?\u118?\u97?\u110?\u105?\u97?}}}{\upr{\*\ud{\title \u68?\u105?\u99?\u97?\u32?\u100?\u101?\u32?\u101?\u115?\u116?\u117?\u100?\u111?\u32?\u8212?\u32?\u68?\u234?\u32?\u118?\u105?\u100?\u97?\u32?\u97?\u111?\u115?\u32?\u114?\u101?\u108?\u97?\u116?\u111?\u115?\u32?\u98?\u237?\u98?\u108?\u105?\u99?\u111?\u115?}}}}\pard\plain\langnp1033\langfenp1033 \ltrpar\s2\qc {\rtlch\fcs1\alang1046\af1\ltrch\fcs0\lang1046\langnp1046\langfe1033\langfenp1033\f0\fs36\cf1\b Dica de estudo }{\rtlch\fcs1\alang1046\af2\ab\ltrch\fcs0\lang1046\langnp1046\langfe1033\langfenp1033\f0\fs36\cf1\b \u8212?}{\rtlch\fcs1\alang1046\af1\ltrch\fcs0\lang1046\langnp1046\langfe1033\langfenp1033\f0\fs36\cf1\b  D\u234? vida aos relatos b\u237?blicos\par}\pard\plain\langnp1033\langfenp1033 \ltrpar\ql\fi576 {\rtlch\fcs1\alang1046\af2\ltrch\fcs0\lang1046\langnp1046\langfe1046\langfenp1046\f2 Na B\u237?blia, encontramos muitos relatos hist\u243?ricos que nos ensinam li\u231?\u245?es importantes. Algo que pode nos ajudar a entender melhor o que estamos lendo e a tirar mais proveito dessas hist\u243?rias \u233? criar imagens mentais. Veja algumas dicas que podem ajudar voc\u234? a dar vida \u224? sua leitura da B\u237?blia.\par}{\rtlch\fcs1\alang1046\af2\ltrch\fcs0\lang1046\langnp1046\langfe1033\langfenp1033\f2 \u8226? }{\rtlch\fcs1\alang1046\af2\ab\ltrch\fcs0\lang1046\langnp1046\langfe1046\langfenp1046\f2\b\i Leia em voz alta.}{\rtlch\fcs1\alang1046\af2\ab\ltrch\fcs0\lang1046\langnp1046\langfe1046\langfenp1046\f2\b  }{\rtlch\fcs1\alang1046\af2\ltrch\fcs0\lang1046\langnp1046\langfe1046\langfenp1046\f2 Ler a B\u237?blia em voz alta pode ajudar voc\u234? a visualizar melhor o que est\u225? lendo. Quando for ler a B\u237?blia em fam\u237?lia, voc\u234? pode pedir para cada um ler um personagem diferente. Isso vai dar ainda mais vida \u224? hist\u243?ria.\par}{\rtlch\fcs1\alang1046\af2\ltrch\fcs0\lang1046\langnp1046\langfe1033\langfenp1033\f2 \u8226? }{\rtlch\fcs1\alang1046\af2\ab\ltrch\fcs0\lang1046\langnp1046\langfe1046\langfenp1046\f2\b\i Imagine a cena.}{\rtlch\fcs1\alang1046\af2\ab\ltrch\fcs0\lang1046\langnp1046\langfe1046\langfenp1046\f2\b  }{\rtlch\fcs1\alang1046\af2\ltrch\fcs0\lang1046\langnp1046\langfe1046\langfenp1046\f2 Tente entender os pensamentos e os sentimentos dos personagens envolvidos. Por exemplo, pergunte-se: \u8216?Por que a pessoa falou ou agiu dessa forma? Se eu estivesse nessa situa\u231?\u227?o, o que eu teria pensado? E como eu teria me sentido?\u8217?\par}{\rtlch\fcs1\alang1046\af2\ltrch\fcs0\lang1046\langnp1046\langfe1033\langfenp1033\f2 \u8226? }{\rtlch\fcs1\alang1046\af2\ab\ltrch\fcs0\lang1046\langnp1046\langfe1046\langfenp1046\f2\b\i Fa\u231?a um desenho.}{\rtlch\fcs1\alang1046\af2\ab\ltrch\fcs0\lang1046\langnp1046\langfe1046\langfenp1046\f2\b  }{\rtlch\fcs1\alang1046\af2\ltrch\fcs0\lang1046\langnp1046\langfe1046\langfenp1046\f2 Desenhar pode ajudar voc\u234? a imaginar melhor as hist\u243?rias da B\u237?blia e n\u227?o se esquecer do que leu, mesmo que o seu desenho n\u227?o seja uma obra de arte.\par}}